I '''Mary Roberts Rinehart''' (Agosto 12, 1876{{spaced ndash}}Setiembre 22, 1958) metung yang [[Estados Unidos|Americana]]ng talasulat libru, a marlas dang ausang Americanang [[Agatha Christie]],<ref name="KEAT">Keating, H.R.F., ''The Bedside Companion to Crime''.  New York: Mysterious Press, 1989, p. 170.  ISBN 0-89296-416-2</ref> oneng misulat ya ing mumunang nang nobelang misteryo labing apat (14) a banwa bayu itang kang Christie.<ref>http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Mysterious_Affair_at_Styles</ref> Ya ing tuturing dang menimbentu king "[[Had I but known|Had-I-But-Known]]" school of mystery writing. Miglalang ya mu namang supercriminal a makasulud ''costume'', a mayayaus "the [[The Bat (pelikulang 1926)|Bat]]", a abanggit nang [[Bob Kane]] a metung kareng inspirasyun ning kayang "[[Batman]]." <ref>[http://asp6new.alexanderstreet.com/atho/atho.detail.people.aspx?personcode=per0045680 Mary Roberts Rinehart - ''North American Theatre Online'']</ref>

